## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="063a5-103">Das <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> -Steuerelement bietet die folgenden Funktionen:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-103">The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> control provides the following capabilities:</span></span>  
  
