## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="063a5-162">Im folgenden Beispiel wird gezeigt, wie eine Skriptfunktion in einem Dokument aus einer [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] -Anwendung mithilfe <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>von aufgerufen wird.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-162">The following example shows how to call a script function in a document from a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="063a5-163">In diesem Beispiel weist die Skriptfunktion keine Parameter auf.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-163">In this example, the script function has no parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="063a5-164">Im folgenden finden Sie [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] das Dokument, das die Skriptfunktion implementiert, die von [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]aufgerufen wird.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-164">The following is the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document that implements the script function that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function called!";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="063a5-165">Das folgende Beispiel zeigt [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] die-Implementierung, um die Skriptfunktion [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] im Dokument aufzurufen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-165">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script function in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters");  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="063a5-173"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>sollte nicht aufgerufen werden, bevor das Dokument, das es implementiert, das Laden abgeschlossen hat.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-173"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="063a5-174">Sie können erkennen, wann das Laden eines Dokuments abgeschlossen ist, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> indem Sie das-Ereignis behandeln.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-174">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="063a5-175">Wenn Sie nicht genügend Parameterwerte an das Skript übergeben, das Sie aufrufen, haben die Parameter, an die Sie keine Werte übergeben, den undefinierten Wert.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-175">If you do not pass enough parameter values to the script that you are invoking, the parameters that you do not pass values to will have the undefined value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="063a5-176">Wenn Sie zu viele Parameterwerte übergeben, werden die überzähligen Werte ignoriert.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-176">If you pass too many parameter values, the excess values are ignored.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="063a5-177">Im folgenden Beispiel wird gezeigt, wie Skriptfunktionen in einem-Dokument aus einer-Anwendung <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>mithilfe von aufgerufen werden.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-177">The following example shows how to call script functions in a document from an application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="063a5-178">In diesem Beispiel erfordern die Skriptfunktionen Parameter.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-178">In this example, the script functions require parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="063a5-179">Im folgenden finden Sie das Dokument, das die Skriptfunktionen implementiert, die von [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]aufgerufen werden.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-179">The following is the document that implements the script functions that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function 'called: " + message + ".";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="063a5-180">Das folgende Beispiel zeigt [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] die-Implementierung zum aufzurufen der Skript [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] Funktionen im Dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-180">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script functions in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters", this.messageTextBox.Text);  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="063a5-194">Der <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> Aufruf von hat denselben Effekt wie das <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> Festlegen der-Eigenschaft.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-194">Calling <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> has the same effect as setting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="063a5-195"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A>wird von Entwicklern verwendet, die deklarativ das ursprüngliche Dokument angeben möchten, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> zu dem navigiert, wenn <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> initialisiert wird.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-195"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> is used from markup by developers who want to declaratively specify the initial document that <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to when <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is initialized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="063a5-196">Verwenden Sie <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> die-Methode, um zu einer URL zu navigieren, die Escapezeichen enthalten kann.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-196">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="063a5-197">Verwenden Sie <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> die-Methode, um <xref:System.Uri> zu einer zu navigieren, die keine Escapezeichen enthält.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-197">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="063a5-198">Im folgenden Beispiel wird gezeigt, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> wie mithilfe der <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> -Methode zu einem Dokument navigiert werden kann.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-198">The following example shows how to use <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> to navigate to a document by using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute. For example, 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="063a5-216">Verwenden Sie <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> die-Methode, um zu einer URL zu navigieren, die Escapezeichen enthalten kann.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-216">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="063a5-217">Verwenden Sie <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> die-Methode, um <xref:System.Uri> zu einer zu navigieren, die keine Escapezeichen enthält.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-217">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="063a5-218">Im folgenden Beispiel wird gezeigt, wie Sie zu einem Dokument navigieren und es in einem neuen Browserfenster öffnen, indem Sie das Ziel "about: blank" angeben.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-218">The following example shows how to navigate to a document and open it in a new browser window by specifying the "about:blank" target.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute. For example, 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri, "_blank", null, null);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="063a5-229">Wenn der `stream` -Parameter `null`ist <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> , wird zu einem leeren Dokument ("about: blank") navigiert.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-229">If the `stream` parameter is `null`, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to a blank document ("about:blank").</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="063a5-230">Wenn der Stream-Parameter nicht in einem gültigen [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] Format vorliegt, wird er als nur-Text angezeigt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-230">If the stream parameter is not in a valid [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] format, it will be displayed as plain text.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="063a5-231">Nach der Navigation <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> ist `null`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-231">After navigation, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> will be `null`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="063a5-232">Im folgenden Beispiel wird gezeigt, wie Sie zu einem Stream navigieren können, der ein Dokument enthält.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="063a5-232">The following example shows how to navigate to a stream that contains a document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateToStreamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Load HTML document as a stream  
  Uri uri = new Uri(@"pack://application:,,,/HTMLDocumentWithScript.html", UriKind.Absolute);  
  Stream source = Application.GetResourceStream(uri).Stream;  
  
  // Navigate to HTML document stream  
  this.webBrowser.NavigateToStream(source);  
}  
```

  
  
